Name:Spiked Trap
Description:Gain <link="se:Spikes">Spikes</link> when losing <link="st:Health">Health</link> 1:1, Lose <link="se:Spikes">Spikes</link> when gaining <link="st:Health">Health</link> 1:1
Rarity:Epic
Stackamount:1
Sizemult:0.35
Tags:[Healing;Selfdamage]
Ability:ApplyStatusEffectSetting(AddAmount:LastIncomingAbilityStats{HealthDamage},StatusEffect:Spikes,ReplaceExistingStacks:False,Unavoidable:True);Target:Self;Trigger:OnReceivingHealthDamage
Ability:ApplyStatusEffectSetting(AddAmount:Multiply{LastIncomingAbilityStats{IncomingHeal},-1},StatusEffect:Spikes,ReplaceExistingStacks:False,Unavoidable:True);Target:Self;Trigger:OnGettingHealed